# Manual

## Languages

- Use the language selector on the top-right: 中文 / 日本語 / English
- APIs accept lang in request body (zh-CN/ja-JP/en-US) to control prompt output language

## Voice

- Use the voice dropdown and Speak/Stop on the top-right
- Uses browser SpeechSynthesis (hidden if not supported)

## FAQ

### No LLM calls

By default llm.enabled=false, so mock output is used.
To enable real LLM output:
- llm.enabled=true
- set llm.base_url / llm.api_key / llm.model

### module/feature is empty

Decomposition expects module/feature fields. Check prompt and model output.
